## handoff

- **Produced:** plan-gate.out with PASS verdict; plan verified complete and research-integrated.
- **Decisions:** No re-routing to pre-researcher needed. Plan covers concept, design system, tech stack, state shape, mock DB schema, file budget, and full traceability matrix.
- **Next needs:** Builder should read pre-researcher.out Section D for all 25 Unsplash URLs and Section E for Leaflet init/sync code snippets; planner.out Sections 3-7 for all build details. Builder must decide mobile split-pane breakpoint behavior (tabs or stacked, ~768px threshold recommended).
- **Risks carried forward:** (1) World-zoom pin overlap at zoom 3 needs local QA pass. (2) Cormorant Garamond at weight 300 may render thin on Windows Chrome -- builder should test and prefer 400 if needed. (3) 13-file budget is firm ceiling; no additional files.

VERDICT: pass
